(1463, 193, 'sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management', 'sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management_questions_project_and_program_management_question_standardized_opportunity_intake_process_it_management=3&sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management_questions_project_and_program_management_sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management_questions_project_and_program_management_question_standardized_opportunity_intake_process_comment=There+is+one+intake+process+for+large+projects+that+exceed+800+hours+or+is+high+risk+or+has+a+political+stance+to+it%2C+there+would+go+to+a+committee+(CTSC)+where+they+are+scored+and+the+committee+decides.+ITS+infrastructure+projects+are+noted+at+this+committee+but+not+decided+by+the+committee.+We+are+in+the+process+of+developing+a+new+intake+process+for+projects+under+the+800+hrs.&sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management_questions_project_and_program_management_question_prioritization___ranking_of_opportunities_it_management=3&sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management_questions_project_and_program_management_sections_it_management_tables_project_and_program_management_questions_project_and_program_management_question_prioritization___ranking_of_opportunities_comment=For+opportunities+that+have+a+legislative+impact%2C+or+are+part+of+a+Council+Report+%E2%80%93+the+prioritization+is+performed+by+Council+directive.+For+opportunities+that+are+of+larger+scale+or+risk%2C+that+affect+more+than+one+department+%E2%80%93+this+is+the+MDI+process.+This+prioritizes+any+project%2C+including+technology+change%2C+that+is+expected+to+have+a+significant+effort+across+more+than+one+department%2C+and+the+governance+and+decision-making+is+performed+by+the+Corporate+Leadership+Team.+For+opportunities+that+do+not+require+either+Council%2C+or+CLT+decision-making%2C+but+are+more+than+800+hours+of+estimated+ITS+time+investment%2C+these+are+prioritized+by+the