(2731, 203, 'information_technology_services_dq_hld', 'desc=The+Information+Technology+(IT)+department+supports+the+Information+Technology%2C+Information+systems+used+and+brings+innovative+solutions+across+the+organization+to+facilitate+the+different+business+units+in+achieving+their+goals.+We+plan+for%2C+implement+and+then+support+IT%2FIS+initiatives+that+provide+security%2C+stability%2C+performance+improvements+and+innovative+solutions+bringing+efficiency\'s+in+processes+and+cost+reductions.+With+the+exception+of+a+very+few+applications+which+are+currently+managed+by+other+business+unit+department+heads%2C+the+IT+department+manages+the+IT+roadmap+to+ensure+the+current+infrastructure+and+applications+meets+the+needs+of+the+business+units+and+brings+forth+new+solutions+that+can+help+the+company+grow.+This+includes+infrastructure%2C+network%2C+telecommunications%2C+telephony+and+application+support%2C+evergreening+and+the+analysis+and+implementation+of+newer+technologies+and+processes+on+the+market+that+can+be+applicable+to+SPI.&reset=true'),
